description:
The Brother Single Bed Color Changer can save you lots of time when working with multiple color. Jump start your creativity with this handy device.<br>
New Brother color changers are no longer available, but I'll bet many knitters have them and have never tried them. There's no time like now!  You'll be surprised at how easy they are to use.<br><br>
The Brother KCC color changer was used for this video on the Brother 970. Not all color changers are interchangeable.

